latestPosts.caption:
Met Gala meets everyday chic! 

For our project, we were challenged to design a garment inspired by the iconic Met Gala, but with a twist - it had to be versatile enough for regular events and everyday wear.
 I took on the challenge and created a two-piece garment featuring a 3D floral jacket paired with a fitted body-con dress with Hand-painted eye and lip shaped pockets.

(Fashion, fashion designer, met gala inspired, fashion designing)

#collegelife #goodvibes #friends #friendsforever #reel #reelitfeelit #reelsofinstagram #goa

Watching my designs come to life on the runway was a dream come true. My theme was inspired by coconut shell and basket weaving as part of art and craft of Goa. 
And the cherry on top? The best accessory award. 🥳
Thanks to my amazing models @spacebound595 @saisha.prabhu  and @naadia.khan22 for bringing my creation to life!💗
